  "title": "WSH Co-Ordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>The company specializes in car park system installation, maintenance, EV car charger installation (Blue SG), car park improvement work including M&E work, and car park customer service.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support workplace safety and health (WSH) by identifying and addressing non-compliances, alerting team members during emergencies, and implementing initiatives to enhance safety programs.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Identify specific workplace safety and health (WSH) non-compliances and unsafe work practices to guide team members in maintaining a safer work environment</li><li>Alert team members promptly during emergency situations and potential incident escalations to enable timely and effective responses</li><li>Implement and support initiatives that improve WSH programs to increase workplace safety awareness and ensure compliance</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to arrange own transport to and from work locations</li><li>Singaporean / SPR Preferred </li></ul>",
